snippet.title: Ash Of Gods OST - Main Menu Music
snippet.description:
The game is avaiable on Steam — add it to your wishlist: http://store.steampowered.com/app/691690/Ash_of_Gods/

Ash of Gods: Redemption (https://ashofgods.com/) is a combination of a dark fantasy visual novel, a Turn-Based RPG and collectible card game with rogue-like gameplay. 

Recorded by www.musicimaginary.com

Music Composed by: Adam Skorupa, Krzysztof Wierzynkiewicz, Michal Cielecki

Instrumentalists:
Vocal: Magdalena Przychodzka
Guitars: Aleksander Grochocki
Fidel: Katarzyna Kamer
